{
  "texts": [
    "In our experiments, we adapted the base code of StructGPT [10] and modified it only for improved reasoning as outlined in the previous section.",
    "We also examined the performance of ChatGPT without RAG on both datasets.",
    "The results, presented in Figure 1, show that Mindful-RAG, shows promising improvement in accuracy of reasoning error cases achieving a Hits@1 of 84% on WebQSP and 82% on MetaQA.",
    "Additional accuracy improvements can be achieved by addressing structural issues and incorporating partial answers to enhance precision, rather than relying solely on exact matches.The primary goal of this study is to explore methods for mitigating reasoning errors in KG-RAG systems.",
    "It is important to emphasize that our approach serves as an initial demonstration of the potential in combining the parametric knowledge of models with non-parametric external knowledge."
  ]
}